      "text": "<p>Jedno vase radio dugme treba da ima <code>value</code> atribut sa vrednoscu <code>indoor</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "const indoorRadioButton = [...document.querySelectorAll('label > input[type=\"radio\"]')].filter(x => x.value === \"indoor\");\nassert.notEmpty(indoorRadioButton)"
    },
